To create a new distribution:

- Install and test changes by running test/run_all.sh
- Update version in configure.ac
- Update top-level README
- Commit your changes:
  commit
  tag .e.g git tag -a v0.3.1 -m 'my version 0.3.1')
  push and push origin --tags
- Run 'python setup.py sdist'
- Upload source and update sourceforge website
OA  keeping the old usage somewhere

